Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H3B3AB6&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Immortal Water Snake Monster, Hydra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18\i1}No dumping{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Youjirou. What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the guardian of\Nthis lake! Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hydra!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough playing around, water snake Hydra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a more important mission\Nthan meddling with ordinary humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I can't stand that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Water snake Hydra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD Supreme Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mission is to disrupt Tokyo's economy.\NProceed with it at once! That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! You doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot better! I should be out in a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Toss it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, be seeing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Up you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? Any pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Oh, mom asked me to tell you\Nshe left this week's fee money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on the table, so you can take it to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whats wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A lizard! There's a lizard there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They creep me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The money and the lizard disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(397.6,58)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\fs54\fscx125\frz5.5\bord0.5\4a&HFF&\3c&H3B3AB6&}New V{\3c&H96653B&}ictoria
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A lizard!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The money's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(64.4,52.8)\fs38\fscx120\frz3\bord5.5\4a&HFF&\3c&HAEB15C&}Toyland\N{\b1\fs74}Pinocchio
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, that'll be ¥500.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My money just disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,M-my money's vanished!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mine's all gone too!\N-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan's off to a great start!\NLet's move on to the second phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a yen left in town...\NIt can only be GOD, can't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're probably trying to upset\Nthe economy rather than make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're bound to aim for\Nan even bigger payoff next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,An even bigger payoff...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18\i1}Tokyo Central Bank service entrance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,F17 here. They just set off as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around, turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs18\i1}Work in progress - Detour{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong?\N-Strange, the car's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, unload the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you guys were behind\Nthe disappearing money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Jin Keisuke?\NIgnore him and unload the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Accursed X Rider, I'll send you to the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You must think you made\Nshort work of Hydra, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised, X Rider?\NHydra's head won't stay cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I was so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hydra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your time.\NYou've already made one mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan's going smoothly!\NWhat mistake!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you blind? Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy at the hospital\Nwitnessed every bit of your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn! So that's where the money went!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Accursed brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Another strange incident has just occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Several hundred million yen was stolen\Nfrom a bank transport vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I wasn't lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's hard to believe...\NA snake monster, melting people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I wasn't lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that blue stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The snake monster!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for you, but you've\Ngotta die now you know our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, curse your interfering ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, they threw the money in the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough out of you, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurse, get Satoru out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:14:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'll make sure you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Take a look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that feel, Rider? Just try moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Shock lets the X Rider instantly pass a thousand-volt\Nelectric current through the surface of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is shocked and sent flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Long Pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The water snake Hydra is immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hydra!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so this is where you hid the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd come all the way down here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it takes to bring that money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'll let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One last time!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Supreme Commander, I'm afraid Hydra has fallen to the X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped. Await reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look! I'm walking already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great. Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider foiled Hydra's plan to disrupt the economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:23:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't be long before GOD are active again.\NDon't lose, Jin Keisuke - X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's Chimera kidnaps a girl with the power\Nto bend spoons and see inside boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And when Rider X tries to save her,\Nhe falls into Chimera's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.60,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the famous spoon-bending boy\NSekiguchi Jun makes an appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next Rider X:\N"Kidnap the Psychic Girl!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
